{"tid":798532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【放工前堅持黃雨】新界北多處嚴重水浸 錦田公路現激流","createTime":"2018-08-29T11:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T17:47:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95ecf3c21f1f1d20746fd2ca0bfeb97fd57fc16e","tid":798532,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535537372_ab6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535537372_ab6f.jpg&h=b52b7d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃雨下新界北區出現水浸，下午5時許，八鄉錦田公路一帶出現嚴重水浸，馬路水深及膝，不少汽車於路中死火。消防及警方於芝麻嶺對開封路，禁止車輛駛入。讀者張小姐表示，下午乘車由錦田公路駛經荃綿公路迴旋處時，目睹大量雨水由大帽山湧落山，馬路變激流。<br />\n<br />\n錦上路蓮花地亦出現嚴重水浸，村內停車場頓成澤國，水深及膝，村民出入須涉水而行。另外，位於八鄉馬鞍崗一間動物暫託中心亦受水浸影響，中心內的水位不斷上升，負責人報警求助。消防員接報趕至，將中心內的動物逐一救出。<br />\n<br />\n天文台於下午5時許表示，屯門區在下午5時正的過去一小時錄得超過70毫米雨量，有可能出現嚴重水浸。新界北部，尤其是八鄉及錦田、上水一帶，正受大雨影響。在過去2小時，該區錄得超過80毫米雨量。<br />\n<br />\n暴雨警告信號現時為黃色，表示香港廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每小時雨量超過30毫米的大雨，且雨勢可能持續。一些低窪地帶及排水欠佳的地區會出現水淹。可能受大雨及水浸影響之市民應採取適當的預防措施，以防止可能引致的損失。<br />\n<br />\n大雨可能引致山洪暴發，市民應遠離河道。可能受河道氾濫影響之市民應採取適當的預防措施，以避免損失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535534870_b2bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535534870_b2bc.jpg&h=65e32484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535536330_b366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535536330_b366.jpg&h=f8a1aee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535536336_4907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535536336_4907.jpg&h=60dd8f83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf929405506e115740e88f755df1230bc76ed73f","tid":798532,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc79a2a7d8f50301d2b2ad1dfd00df533622222a","tid":798532,"uid":31758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a613904f5465ca210c797825fadc55d15214d72","tid":798532,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"天文台堅持黃雨, 但大埔已陸沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XvRELn4.IjUlCG8HdVOvNQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180829a145708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXvRELn4.IjUlCG8HdVOvNQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180829a145708.jpg&h=22e47318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色暴雨警告生效，有多名網民在Facebook群組大埔發相，見到南運路一帶，出現嚴重水浸恍如黃河， 黃泥水大量湧出，多輛汽車被困。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有網民見到在大埔墟車站附近的行人隧道，被黃泥水淹沒。除了大埔市中心，大尾篤也有市民見到村内馬路變成急流。<br />\n<br />\n天文台下午2時25分發出局部地區大雨報告，大埔區在下午2時20分的過去一小時錄得超過70毫米雨量，有可能出現嚴重水浸。可能受大雨影響之市民，應採取適當的預防措施，以防止水浸可能引致的損失。大雨可能引致山洪暴發，市民應遠離河道。駕駛人士應注意道路可能出現嚴重水浸及交通擠塞"},{"pid":"720bfd8e20c92579285d7582451864ae36a4a3fe","tid":798532,"uid":124410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"根本大交合成個部門呃飯食<br />\n你屌佢又用專業決定來回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c1fae0a54a8debdd002e7e37758a66920eeedd","tid":798532,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"黃雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ca22cfce3979388370eb453e05c9d8c0c8c4a7","tid":798532,"uid":187076,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/191021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F191021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1c79b102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74a9b219a67d9c7b4cde5e9f8e6c0a9f3f79e53e","tid":798532,"uid":85818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"激流咁款<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nGuRGXnsxJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnGuRGXnsxJE&d=uvwrVu6glWXiFcrT12S%2BzjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c0233871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nGuRGXnsxJE</a>"},{"pid":"e326088b236e81748fbf3f3aa35d78226b48310c","tid":798532,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"民間氣象組織「香港地下天文台」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 指，截至下午5時，石崗一帶已錄得超過200毫米雨量；單計下午3時45分至4時45時的短短1小時，元朗錄得的雨量高達119毫米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535540991_b030.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535540991_b030.png&h=f95e3a96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"530a4d0d92e6170211596edab2aa319e4d6efa57","tid":798532,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e326088b236e81748fbf3f3aa35d78226b48310c","tid":798532,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13